  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I spoke about my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I spoke about the devilish sights. 'Even in moments of joy, there hides an insidious catch, my father's bleeding fingers mending my yellow patch.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was a man of peace, a dreamer locked up in his dream, with an open, generous hand, though his pockets were lean.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He toiled all his life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But money was not his god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Lest his earned penny bring relief, he would rather choke on his lot.' Well, this gives you more a picture of my father, what sort of man he was. 'And then my mother, my sweet little mother, her story an obvious trial, and yet her eyes spark with hope, her lips a lingering smile.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She loved the open space at the early break of dawn, and sung of twilight shadows when this sun was gone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I also had two sisters, mothers in their prime of life-- Ida, the gentle dove, and Pola, the rebel in strife.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they, my two little nieces, [? butts ?] of a miscarried spring, never permitted to play, verboten to sing.'",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this gives you more of a picture of ghetto, what-- how my life was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will not continue with that because this is a long poem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It might take me another 10, 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But just to go back to the issue of language.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this poem, in 'No Exit--'",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
